reviewText: Love this show wish there were more seasons
I simply love this show.  I wish it was still on the air.

This DVD of Hutterites was exactly what I had seen on TV and met all my expectations.  I really like the episodes following one another, so I don't have to stop and click on the episode I want.  I can watch this DVD for hours!!!  Love it!!!

The characters are more real than the most of people I meet every day.
 I feel I know Wesley, Claudia, Clinton and Bertha.
It was great!
